channel.title: Fastest way to level 45 Farming to 54?
channel.description: I would like to know what the fastest way to get up farming would be. I have 45 farming currently and run from Ardougne Patch to Falador Patch and Tree Patch to Catherby Patch and Fruit Tree Patch. The trees take ages but do give good amounts of xp... i am working on level 54 farming and all other skills required to do the Fairy Tales Part II and IV. Please post advice. I use Strawberries, Limpwurts, Harralanders, Willow Tree and Orange Tree...
